1
00:01:32,110 --> 00:01:34,990
[How dare you!?]

2
00:01:35,030 --> 00:01:39,880
[Episode 21]

3
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:02,560
Push harder!

4
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,600
Bring the battering ram!

5
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:06,200
Yes!

6
00:02:16,750 --> 00:02:18,610
You're at the end of your rope now,

7
00:02:18,630 --> 00:02:19,910
and you're still not giving up?

8
00:02:19,910 --> 00:02:20,280
Dan.

9
00:02:21,710 --> 00:02:22,770
Should we kill her?

10
00:02:29,710 --> 00:02:30,970
Do you have any poison?

11
00:02:31,750 --> 00:02:33,710
The kind
that won't kill someone right away.

12
00:02:33,710 --> 00:02:35,110
How do you know I have any?

13
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:42,120
I didn't make it myself.

14
00:02:42,910 --> 00:02:44,440
I don't know if it's lethal.

15
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,810
But I tested it on a chicken.

16
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:49,700
One pill shouldn't kill a person.

17
00:02:49,910 --> 00:02:51,170
When the chicken ate it

18
00:02:51,190 --> 00:02:52,400
it collapsed immediately.

19
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,030
Mr. Bei,

20
00:02:54,590 --> 00:02:56,410
Feed this to the Empress Dowager.

21
00:02:56,410 --> 00:02:57,070
Xiahou Dan!

22
00:03:01,470 --> 00:03:02,130
Xiahou Dan!

23
00:03:02,750 --> 00:03:04,410
Xiahou Dan, you can't kill me!

24
00:03:04,430 --> 00:03:05,700
I raised you!

25
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:07,600
I put you where you are today!

26
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,190
Dan.

27
00:03:11,470 --> 00:03:12,000
Dan...

28
00:03:13,260 --> 00:03:14,270
Xiahou Dan!

29
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:16,579
You've been poisoned.

30
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:17,560
If I die,

31
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,450
you'll die too.

32
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,470
The throne of Great Xia

33
00:03:21,470 --> 00:03:22,870
will belong to Xiahou Po.

34
00:03:23,010 --> 00:03:24,140
Dan, think about it.

35
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:25,310
Are we

36
00:03:25,910 --> 00:03:27,020
going to hand over

37
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:29,070
the empire to him so easily?

38
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:31,490
Mother, you seem to have forgotten

39
00:03:32,710 --> 00:03:34,640
that thanks to you and Prince Duan,

40
00:03:35,750 --> 00:03:38,210
I've been poisoned many times
over the years

41
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,600
and taken so many medicines.

42
00:03:41,610 --> 00:03:42,860
Ordinary poisons

43
00:03:43,750 --> 00:03:45,240
no longer affect me.

44
00:03:47,050 --> 00:03:48,940
So Mother, don't worry.

45
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:52,170
I won't die before you.

46
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:54,530
Feed it to the Empress Dowager.

47
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:15,300
Mother, do you remember where we are?

48
00:04:19,980 --> 00:04:23,050
In the tomb
I built for you with my own hands.

49
00:04:39,200 --> 00:04:40,360
The door has been broken down!

50
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,620
The Emperor is inside!

51
00:04:41,750 --> 00:04:42,360
Kill them!

52
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:05,980
Your Highness!

53
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:17,140
I, Fu He, Deputy Commander
of the Imperial Guards,

54
00:05:17,140 --> 00:05:18,120
was late in coming to the rescue.

55
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:20,050
I beg Your Majesty's forgiveness!

56
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:22,000
I'm fine.

57
00:05:25,070 --> 00:05:27,070
Quickly, save the Empress Dowager.

58
00:05:31,510 --> 00:05:32,370
Your Highness!

59
00:05:32,390 --> 00:05:33,159
Your Highness!

60
00:05:33,159 --> 00:05:34,890
Terrible news, Your Highness!

61
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,800
Terrible news!

62
00:05:38,870 --> 00:05:39,720
Speak.

63
00:05:41,310 --> 00:05:42,180
Tu'er

64
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:43,909
had already

65
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:46,550
depleted most of the Emperor's forces.

66
00:05:46,630 --> 00:05:48,360
We seized the chance to strike.

67
00:05:48,630 --> 00:05:49,120
But

68
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:50,780
unexpectedly,

69
00:05:51,159 --> 00:05:52,040
the Imperial Guards

70
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,800
suddenly appeared out of nowhere.

71
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:56,840
All our efforts are wasted!

72
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:07,920
Isn't Zhao Wucheng on our side?

73
00:06:08,870 --> 00:06:10,530
He wasn't leading the troops.

74
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:12,670
It's said the deputy commander

75
00:06:12,870 --> 00:06:16,330
used the Tiger Tally to mobilize
the army without permission.

76
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:19,450
What about the Emperor?

77
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:23,800
Was he injured?

78
00:06:24,270 --> 00:06:24,730
Well...

79
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,390
I

80
00:06:26,870 --> 00:06:28,300
was lucky enough

81
00:06:28,750 --> 00:06:29,950
to escape alive.

82
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:42,460
[Capital of Xia]

83
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,010
Stop.

84
00:06:53,180 --> 00:06:54,510
Deputy Commander Fu He.

85
00:06:57,409 --> 00:06:57,950
Move!

86
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:00,960
Your Majesty.

87
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:06,620
Where is Zhao Wucheng?

88
00:07:07,950 --> 00:07:08,270
I...

89
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,140
His Majesty is asking you!

90
00:07:12,780 --> 00:07:13,840
Commander Zhao...

91
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:15,680
has gone missing.

92
00:07:16,070 --> 00:07:17,120
Issue my decree:

93
00:07:19,070 --> 00:07:21,660
Zhao Wucheng,
Commander of the Imperial Guards,

94
00:07:21,660 --> 00:07:23,520
has committed insubordination,

95
00:07:23,870 --> 00:07:25,530
neglected his duty, and fled,

96
00:07:25,540 --> 00:07:28,200
causing the Empress Dowager's
sudden illness.

97
00:07:29,430 --> 00:07:30,920
Dismiss him immediately

98
00:07:31,750 --> 00:07:33,680
and search the entire city for him.

99
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:34,510
I...

100
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,190
want him alive.

101
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:39,040
Yes.

102
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:41,810
Deputy Commander Fu He.

103
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:43,850
I am here.

104
00:07:44,159 --> 00:07:45,690
For your merit in saving me,

105
00:07:46,500 --> 00:07:48,230
you are promoted to Commander,

106
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:50,820
Grand General of the Junior Second Rank,

107
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:53,450
with full command of the Imperial Guards.

108
00:07:54,730 --> 00:07:55,330
Thank you,

109
00:07:55,630 --> 00:07:57,630
Your Majesty, for this great honor.

110
00:07:58,490 --> 00:07:59,350
Your Highness.

111
00:07:59,950 --> 00:08:01,310
The Emperor appeared at the city gate.

112
00:08:01,310 --> 00:08:03,040
He promoted Deputy Commander Fu He.

113
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:04,480
But he didn't get out of his carriage.

114
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,000
I

115
00:08:05,510 --> 00:08:07,240
couldn't tell if he's injured.

116
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:10,720
Tu'er.

117
00:08:12,510 --> 00:08:14,110
What about those assassins?

118
00:08:14,430 --> 00:08:16,030
They're nowhere to be found.

119
00:08:16,070 --> 00:08:18,200
We don't know if they are alive or dead.

120
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:36,270
Xiahou Dan!

121
00:08:37,909 --> 00:08:40,460
You're really hard to kill!

122
00:08:41,150 --> 00:08:43,490
You're really hard to kill!

123
00:08:49,790 --> 00:08:51,550
Issue an order in His Majesty's name:

124
00:08:51,550 --> 00:08:52,720
the palace is under curfew tonight.

125
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:53,840
No one may enter or leave.

126
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:54,150
Yes.

127
00:08:57,930 --> 00:08:58,320
Here.

128
00:08:59,910 --> 00:09:00,440
Careful.

129
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:05,730
Alright.

130
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:09,960
Hang in there.

131
00:09:10,590 --> 00:09:11,670
I'll go fetch the imperial physicians.

132
00:09:11,670 --> 00:09:12,200
Don't go.

133
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:15,630
The Imperial Medical Bureau

134
00:09:15,630 --> 00:09:17,360
is full of Prince Duan's spies.

135
00:09:18,160 --> 00:09:20,120
If he finds out I'm injured,

136
00:09:21,390 --> 00:09:23,120
the peace talks will be ruined.

137
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,190
Don't worry.

138
00:09:37,550 --> 00:09:38,910
I'm just a little tired.

139
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:48,250
You don't need to worry either.

140
00:09:48,780 --> 00:09:49,640
I can handle it.

141
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:53,600
Mr. Bei,

142
00:09:54,890 --> 00:09:56,020
can you manage this?

143
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:59,000
I can only stop the bleeding temporarily.

144
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,580
But he's been poisoned.

145
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:02,150
The wound won't heal.

146
00:10:02,270 --> 00:10:03,270
What should we do?

147
00:10:04,030 --> 00:10:05,160
Who else can we find?

148
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:09,780
Lan.

149
00:10:11,250 --> 00:10:12,380
Go find Consort Xie.

150
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:13,700
Tell her to avoid Prince Duan's spies...

151
00:10:13,700 --> 00:10:14,080
Yes.

152
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:15,790
And bring Xiao Tiancai here secretly.

153
00:10:15,790 --> 00:10:16,510
If she doesn't believe you...

154
00:10:16,510 --> 00:10:16,840
Okay.

155
00:10:17,130 --> 00:10:18,790
Just make this gesture to her.

156
00:10:19,390 --> 00:10:19,920
Hurry up.

157
00:10:20,870 --> 00:10:22,400
Be careful, Your Highness.

158
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:25,210
Gently.

159
00:10:26,150 --> 00:10:27,120
Consort Xie,

160
00:10:27,790 --> 00:10:29,300
with what you're doing now,

161
00:10:29,300 --> 00:10:29,630
I...

162
00:10:29,750 --> 00:10:30,240
Shut up.

163
00:10:30,910 --> 00:10:31,750
Be quiet.

164
00:10:33,040 --> 00:10:34,190
If you yell,

165
00:10:34,210 --> 00:10:35,270
I'll hit you again.

166
00:10:41,930 --> 00:10:42,990
What are you doing?

167
00:10:45,900 --> 00:10:47,280
You talk too much.

168
00:10:48,910 --> 00:10:49,900
Consort Xie.

169
00:10:50,030 --> 00:10:51,030
Consort Xie.

170
00:10:51,270 --> 00:10:54,070
-I'm Lan, Noble Consort's personal maid.
-Lan...

171
00:10:57,030 --> 00:10:58,390
What is it?

172
00:10:59,670 --> 00:11:02,080
Noble Consort asks you
to go to Yongyan Palace with me.

173
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:03,360
She also said to bring along

174
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:06,420
that junior imperial physician
you're familiar with.

175
00:11:06,910 --> 00:11:08,030
I don't have any

176
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:10,480
familiar physicians in the palace.

177
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:12,250
Besides,

178
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:15,570
I'm not feeling well tonight

179
00:11:15,790 --> 00:11:17,000
and am already resting.

180
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:17,800
Please leave.

181
00:11:18,190 --> 00:11:20,030
Noble Consort
also asked me to give you a message,

182
00:11:20,030 --> 00:11:20,690
which is...

183
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:29,600
"GA-VE-ME-FI-VE."

184
00:11:35,110 --> 00:11:36,470
But I do like someone.

185
00:11:36,550 --> 00:11:36,960
Who?

186
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:37,740
Give me five.

187
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:39,890
Give me five?

188
00:11:42,280 --> 00:11:43,140
Oh my goodness!

189
00:11:43,890 --> 00:11:45,100
I was so scared.

190
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:46,880
Yu Wanyin,

191
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:49,380
you're finally back.

192
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:54,270
We couldn't find them.

193
00:11:54,270 --> 00:11:55,270
Search over there.

194
00:11:55,270 --> 00:11:56,670
You guys, search the back!

195
00:11:56,670 --> 00:11:57,200
Let's go!

196
00:12:19,790 --> 00:12:20,320
Yong'er.

197
00:12:20,670 --> 00:12:21,150
Wanyin,

198
00:12:21,420 --> 00:12:22,620
you're finally back.

199
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:25,290
This is Physician Xiao.

200
00:12:25,880 --> 00:12:26,720
Physician Xiao,

201
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:27,720
His Majesty has been poisoned.

202
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:29,510
His wound won't heal and keeps bleeding.

203
00:12:29,510 --> 00:12:30,510
Please save him.

204
00:12:31,630 --> 00:12:32,670
I will do my utmost.

205
00:12:32,670 --> 00:12:33,330
Physician.

206
00:12:40,680 --> 00:12:42,340
It didn't hit any vital spots.

207
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:43,240
What should I do?

208
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:43,770
You...

209
00:12:44,090 --> 00:12:45,290
Hold the wound first.

210
00:12:47,910 --> 00:12:49,240
What exactly happened?

211
00:12:49,390 --> 00:12:50,240
How did it get this bad?

212
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:51,170
Are you alright?

213
00:12:51,270 --> 00:12:52,730
A few words can't explain.

214
00:12:52,790 --> 00:12:53,320
In short,

215
00:12:54,120 --> 00:12:55,120
the Empress Dowager has collapsed.

216
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:56,120
We barely made it.

217
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:58,970
As long as we survive the next few days,

218
00:12:59,150 --> 00:13:01,080
we'll be able to fight Prince Duan.

219
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:05,260
But can he survive such a serious injury?

220
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:09,720
What am I even saying?

221
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:10,650
Of course he can.

222
00:13:11,630 --> 00:13:12,030
Right.

223
00:13:12,670 --> 00:13:14,800
We could give him a blood transfusion.

224
00:13:15,550 --> 00:13:17,150
We don't know his blood type.

225
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:18,320
I'm type O.

226
00:13:18,750 --> 00:13:19,750
Universal donor.

227
00:13:20,510 --> 00:13:21,500
You mean

228
00:13:21,550 --> 00:13:23,480
you were type O before coming here?

229
00:13:24,270 --> 00:13:24,870
Oh, right.

230
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:28,250
Yong'er,

231
00:13:29,030 --> 00:13:31,090
I haven't had the chance to thank you.

232
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:33,480
If you hadn't risked yourself
to deliver that message,

233
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:35,410
we might all have died at Mount Bei.

234
00:13:35,550 --> 00:13:37,480
I just made the choice I wanted.

235
00:13:39,150 --> 00:13:40,080
Enough about me.

236
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:41,550
I'm curious—

237
00:13:41,570 --> 00:13:42,550
you don't know martial arts.

238
00:13:42,550 --> 00:13:43,610
How did you escape?

239
00:13:50,750 --> 00:13:51,600
A gun?

240
00:13:52,390 --> 00:13:53,320
That's a choice?

241
00:13:54,670 --> 00:13:55,550
My goodness.

242
00:13:56,270 --> 00:13:58,400
I'm glad I'm not standing against you.

243
00:14:02,870 --> 00:14:03,730
Your Highness.

244
00:14:03,830 --> 00:14:04,760
Physician Xiao,

245
00:14:04,870 --> 00:14:05,720
how is it?

246
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:07,880
Judging from the wound,

247
00:14:08,510 --> 00:14:09,830
His Majesty
seems to have been poisoned with

248
00:14:09,830 --> 00:14:12,510
a toxin that prevents blood clotting
and healing.

249
00:14:12,510 --> 00:14:14,050
This poison is extremely potent

250
00:14:14,050 --> 00:14:15,840
and doesn't seem to be from our Great Xia.

251
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:16,640
That's right.

252
00:14:16,910 --> 00:14:18,170
It's from Qiang State.

253
00:14:19,120 --> 00:14:22,180
But there's more than one poison
in His Majesty's body.

254
00:14:23,150 --> 00:14:24,630
Your Highness, please don't panic.

255
00:14:24,630 --> 00:14:26,600
Although the old poison
has built up over many years,

256
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:27,460
it's not fatal.

257
00:14:28,150 --> 00:14:30,390
I've long heard that His Majesty
suffers from headaches.

258
00:14:30,390 --> 00:14:32,510
They are most likely
related to this poison.

259
00:14:32,510 --> 00:14:33,370
Is there a cure?

260
00:14:33,630 --> 00:14:34,600
I need time.

261
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:36,020
However...

262
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:36,670
What?

263
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:38,800
There's something strange.

264
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:40,510
As you said earlier,

265
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:43,320
this new poison should cause the wound
to continue worsening.

266
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:44,870
But from what I just observed,

267
00:14:44,870 --> 00:14:46,840
when the new poison interacted
with the old one,

268
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:49,300
the wound actually
showed signs of healing.

269
00:14:49,440 --> 00:14:51,150
I'm a bit confused.

270
00:14:51,840 --> 00:14:53,370
What exactly is happening?

271
00:14:53,550 --> 00:14:55,480
There's only one possibility now:

272
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:57,310
the new poison and the old poison

273
00:14:57,310 --> 00:14:58,770
counteracted each other.

274
00:14:59,550 --> 00:15:00,210
You mean...

275
00:15:01,390 --> 00:15:02,680
curing poison with poison?

276
00:15:02,680 --> 00:15:03,210
Exactly.

277
00:15:06,550 --> 00:15:07,200
Empress Dowager.

278
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:09,120
Let me check your pulse.
Please don't move.

279
00:15:09,120 --> 00:15:10,440
Come on. Hold her down for me.

280
00:15:10,440 --> 00:15:11,910
Why are you dawdling?

281
00:15:12,020 --> 00:15:12,680
Hurry!

282
00:15:12,790 --> 00:15:13,120
Yes.

283
00:15:14,680 --> 00:15:15,910
Come on. Help me hold her hand.

284
00:15:15,910 --> 00:15:16,710
Acupuncture!

285
00:15:17,080 --> 00:15:17,880
Acupuncture!

286
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:23,310
Don't worry, Your Majesty.

287
00:15:23,310 --> 00:15:25,570
The imperial physician is treating her.

288
00:16:14,750 --> 00:16:16,010
You're finally awake.

289
00:16:19,120 --> 00:16:20,320
How long was I asleep?

290
00:16:20,750 --> 00:16:21,680
A day and a night.

291
00:16:21,790 --> 00:16:23,050
You scared me to death.

292
00:16:24,960 --> 00:16:26,200
How do you feel now?

293
00:16:36,480 --> 00:16:37,810
Better than I expected.

294
00:16:39,200 --> 00:16:40,670
Mr. Bei made you some sweet porridge.

295
00:16:40,670 --> 00:16:41,800
Try to have a little.

296
00:16:58,030 --> 00:16:59,630
How are things at the palace?

297
00:17:00,240 --> 00:17:01,750
Court was not held yesterday.

298
00:17:01,750 --> 00:17:02,870
The official story is that

299
00:17:02,870 --> 00:17:05,030
you were attending
to the Empress Dowager's illness.

300
00:17:05,030 --> 00:17:07,230
The palace gates are still restricted.

301
00:17:07,510 --> 00:17:09,240
But I wanted to bluff Prince Duan,

302
00:17:09,240 --> 00:17:09,640
so

303
00:17:10,030 --> 00:17:12,069
I had them prepare for the peace talks

304
00:17:12,069 --> 00:17:14,130
as scheduled the day after tomorrow.

305
00:17:14,920 --> 00:17:15,819
There's been

306
00:17:16,200 --> 00:17:18,460
no movement from Prince Duan's side yet.

307
00:17:18,640 --> 00:17:19,880
What about the Empress Dowager?

308
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:21,589
I heard she's been shouting nonstop

309
00:17:21,589 --> 00:17:23,250
and can barely speak clearly.

310
00:17:24,680 --> 00:17:26,810
As for the officials from her faction,

311
00:17:27,030 --> 00:17:29,030
they've been coming to me
one after another

312
00:17:29,030 --> 00:17:31,110
like the Calabash Brothers
rescuing their grandfather.

313
00:17:31,110 --> 00:17:33,830
But Xie Yong'er sent them all away
with just a few words.

314
00:17:33,830 --> 00:17:35,630
Xie Yong'er is that formidable?

315
00:17:37,510 --> 00:17:38,960
When women unite

316
00:17:39,070 --> 00:17:40,440
and work on something important,

317
00:17:40,440 --> 00:17:42,300
they're no less capable than men.

318
00:17:44,510 --> 00:17:46,240
You really scared me with this.

319
00:17:46,510 --> 00:17:48,170
If she hadn't been helping me,

320
00:17:48,590 --> 00:17:51,120
I definitely
couldn't have handled it alone.

321
00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:54,420
You haven't rested at all?

322
00:17:55,480 --> 00:17:56,110
I'm fine.

323
00:17:57,550 --> 00:17:58,660
Seeing you awake

324
00:17:58,750 --> 00:17:59,880
puts my mind at ease.

325
00:18:01,240 --> 00:18:01,960
Well, I'll...

326
00:18:01,960 --> 00:18:03,490
You're not going anywhere.

327
00:18:05,350 --> 00:18:06,350
Sleep for a while.

328
00:18:07,350 --> 00:18:09,270
Just consider it keeping me company.

329
00:18:09,270 --> 00:18:11,750
I can't. There are
still many things to take care of.

330
00:18:11,750 --> 00:18:12,960
If you fall ill too,

331
00:18:12,390 --> 00:18:14,500
♪ A letter, a line of words ♪

332
00:18:13,960 --> 00:18:14,920
I'll really have no one to rely on,

333
00:18:14,820 --> 00:18:16,050
♪ Picking up the pen again and again ♪

334
00:18:16,400 --> 00:18:18,580
♪ A cup of tea, a glass of wine ♪

335
00:18:16,590 --> 00:18:18,250
inside or outside the palace.

336
00:18:18,850 --> 00:18:20,360
♪ Drinking alone, hard to get drunk ♪

337
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:22,740
♪ Words unspoken ♪

338
00:18:23,510 --> 00:18:23,840
Okay.

339
00:18:24,300 --> 00:18:26,750
♪ Shyness unhidden ♪

340
00:18:24,920 --> 00:18:26,480
Then you should get some more sleep too.

341
00:18:26,480 --> 00:18:27,550
Physician Xiao said

342
00:18:27,550 --> 00:18:28,750
sleep is the best medicine.

343
00:18:28,420 --> 00:18:30,570
♪ Walking down a street together ♪

344
00:18:30,030 --> 00:18:30,750
I'll do as you say, Wanyin.

345
00:18:30,750 --> 00:18:31,910
♪ Shoulder to shoulder ♪

346
00:18:32,310 --> 00:18:32,790
Lie down.

347
00:18:32,380 --> 00:18:34,390
♪ Raising my head, lowering my eyes ♪

348
00:18:34,860 --> 00:18:36,220
♪ Blushing slightly ♪

349
00:18:36,320 --> 00:18:38,820
♪ A face flushed red at first sight ♪

350
00:18:40,320 --> 00:18:43,660
♪ A smile like a flower in my heart ♪

351
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:47,670
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

352
00:18:48,340 --> 00:18:51,330
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

353
00:18:49,880 --> 00:18:50,540
Go to sleep.

354
00:18:51,770 --> 00:18:53,670
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

355
00:18:53,900 --> 00:18:55,580
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

356
00:18:55,840 --> 00:18:57,500
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

357
00:18:57,850 --> 00:18:59,950
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

358
00:19:00,370 --> 00:19:03,520
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

359
00:19:04,400 --> 00:19:06,730
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

360
00:19:06,800 --> 00:19:07,950
♪ Still unchanged ♪

361
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:08,400
Sleep.

362
00:19:08,410 --> 00:19:11,270
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

363
00:19:11,870 --> 00:19:13,320
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

364
00:19:13,430 --> 00:19:20,700
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

365
00:19:32,740 --> 00:19:38,170
[Taiji Hall]

366
00:19:34,170 --> 00:19:35,230
Mr. Mu, wait!

367
00:19:36,640 --> 00:19:37,070
Mr. Mu!

368
00:19:39,200 --> 00:19:40,000
Mr. Mu!

369
00:19:40,830 --> 00:19:42,790
The more I called you, the faster you ran.

370
00:19:42,790 --> 00:19:43,590
Let me ask you.

371
00:19:43,960 --> 00:19:46,110
Didn't they say the Empress Dowager
was just a little startled?

372
00:19:46,110 --> 00:19:47,550
How come His Majesty
attended to her yesterday

373
00:19:47,550 --> 00:19:48,550
and today as well?

374
00:19:48,750 --> 00:19:50,160
This must be a serious illness

375
00:19:50,160 --> 00:19:51,620
if he's not holding court.

376
00:19:52,030 --> 00:19:52,640
Mr. Chen,

377
00:19:53,440 --> 00:19:55,110
I don't know either.

378
00:19:56,070 --> 00:19:57,110
How can you not know?

379
00:19:57,110 --> 00:19:58,170
Wasn't this your i—

380
00:20:02,030 --> 00:20:04,480
Wasn't the Empress Dowager's trip
to Mount Bei your idea?

381
00:20:04,480 --> 00:20:06,000
Now the envoy delegation is missing,

382
00:20:06,000 --> 00:20:07,350
the Empress Dowager
and His Majesty are missing,

383
00:20:07,350 --> 00:20:09,150
and even Prince Duan is missing.

384
00:20:09,200 --> 00:20:10,260
This isn't normal.

385
00:20:10,590 --> 00:20:11,200
Lord Chen,

386
00:20:12,160 --> 00:20:12,890
why don't you

387
00:20:13,070 --> 00:20:15,790
go to the Empress Dowager's chamber
yourself and ask?

388
00:20:15,790 --> 00:20:17,450
Then you'll know everything.

389
00:20:22,640 --> 00:20:23,040
You...

390
00:20:23,880 --> 00:20:25,960
The Imperial Guards and the Yulin Guards
fought in the streets!

391
00:20:25,960 --> 00:20:26,720
Such a serious matter—

392
00:20:26,720 --> 00:20:28,310
I must inform Her Majesty!

393
00:20:28,510 --> 00:20:30,310
-Yes, we should tell her!
-Yes!

394
00:20:30,310 --> 00:20:30,590
Indeed.

395
00:20:30,590 --> 00:20:31,680
The envoy delegation has disappeared.

396
00:20:31,680 --> 00:20:32,790
It involves diplomatic relations.

397
00:20:32,790 --> 00:20:34,190
Can you afford the delay?

398
00:20:34,310 --> 00:20:34,740
Exactly!

399
00:20:34,740 --> 00:20:36,200
-By order of His Majesty,
-Can you afford the delay?

400
00:20:36,200 --> 00:20:37,720
the Empress Dowager
has suddenly fallen seriously ill

401
00:20:37,720 --> 00:20:38,590
and must rest.

402
00:20:38,880 --> 00:20:40,210
No one is to disturb her.

403
00:20:40,680 --> 00:20:41,140
This...

404
00:20:41,160 --> 00:20:42,590
You keep repeating yourself.

405
00:20:42,590 --> 00:20:43,550
Is that all you can say?

406
00:20:43,380 --> 00:20:49,220
[Shou'an Palace]

407
00:20:43,640 --> 00:20:44,640
-Move!
-Back off!

408
00:20:44,750 --> 00:20:45,160
Move!

409
00:20:45,400 --> 00:20:45,790
Move!

410
00:20:46,070 --> 00:20:47,310
I'll stay here today.

411
00:20:47,550 --> 00:20:49,000
What are you going to do about it?

412
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:49,440
Exactly!

413
00:20:49,440 --> 00:20:49,800
Right!

414
00:20:49,800 --> 00:20:50,830
What can you do about us?

415
00:20:50,830 --> 00:20:51,240
Exactly!

416
00:20:51,240 --> 00:20:52,390
Quick, let us in!

417
00:20:53,310 --> 00:20:53,930
Mr. Chen.

418
00:20:54,110 --> 00:20:54,510
Clam down.

419
00:20:54,510 --> 00:20:55,720
-Mr. Chen is here.
-Calm down.

420
00:20:55,720 --> 00:20:56,580
Step aside now!

421
00:20:56,680 --> 00:20:58,070
Mr. Chen, you're finally here.

422
00:20:58,070 --> 00:20:59,570
They won't let us in.

423
00:20:59,660 --> 00:21:00,070
Right.

424
00:21:00,070 --> 00:21:00,670
Calm down.

425
00:21:01,510 --> 00:21:02,840
By order of His Majesty,

426
00:21:03,110 --> 00:21:04,750
the Empress Dowager
has suddenly fallen seriously ill.

427
00:21:04,750 --> 00:21:06,080
No one is to disturb her.

428
00:21:06,240 --> 00:21:06,970
How dare you!

429
00:21:07,510 --> 00:21:09,440
Open your eyes and look carefully!

430
00:21:09,480 --> 00:21:11,480
This is Mr. Chen Danian,
Minister of Revenue,

431
00:21:11,480 --> 00:21:13,680
the Empress Dowager's
most trusted official.

432
00:21:13,680 --> 00:21:14,240
Exactly!

433
00:21:14,240 --> 00:21:15,440
Yes, this is Mr. Chen.

434
00:21:17,200 --> 00:21:17,880
Young sir,

435
00:21:18,270 --> 00:21:19,680
the Empress Dowager once instructed

436
00:21:19,680 --> 00:21:20,790
that as soon as
she returned to the palace,

437
00:21:20,790 --> 00:21:22,790
I must come to meet her immediately.

438
00:21:23,030 --> 00:21:23,830
Immediately.

439
00:21:27,000 --> 00:21:27,530
Mr. Chen!

440
00:21:28,480 --> 00:21:29,810
By order of His Majesty,

441
00:21:29,880 --> 00:21:32,050
no one is to disturb Her Majesty.

442
00:21:32,720 --> 00:21:33,740
No one.

443
00:21:34,110 --> 00:21:34,510
You...

444
00:21:37,170 --> 00:21:45,030
[Prince Duan's Mansion]

445
00:21:37,510 --> 00:21:39,070
The Imperial Guards provoked us first.

446
00:21:39,070 --> 00:21:40,680
Many civilians witnessed it.

447
00:21:40,680 --> 00:21:42,070
Public opinion is in uproar now.

448
00:21:42,070 --> 00:21:43,920
What should we do?

449
00:21:44,310 --> 00:21:44,720
Yes.

450
00:21:45,270 --> 00:21:46,330
Everyone is saying

451
00:21:46,350 --> 00:21:48,210
that the Emperor was injured too.

452
00:21:48,240 --> 00:21:49,700
Regarding the next steps,

453
00:21:49,720 --> 00:21:51,580
we need to meet with His Highness.

454
00:21:52,830 --> 00:21:53,920
I understand

455
00:21:54,110 --> 00:21:55,040
how you all feel.

456
00:21:55,480 --> 00:21:57,270
But His Highness
has been unwell these days

457
00:21:57,270 --> 00:21:58,670
and isn't seeing anyone.

458
00:21:59,440 --> 00:21:59,970
My Lords,

459
00:22:00,480 --> 00:22:00,970
my apologies.

460
00:22:00,970 --> 00:22:06,180
[Prince Duan's Mansion]

461
00:22:02,070 --> 00:22:02,530
Well...

462
00:22:04,880 --> 00:22:05,340
Well...

463
00:22:05,640 --> 00:22:06,110
Wait!

464
00:22:06,590 --> 00:22:07,000
Wait!

465
00:22:08,480 --> 00:22:08,940
Hold on.

466
00:22:10,830 --> 00:22:11,760
Why are you here?

467
00:22:13,550 --> 00:22:15,680
Wasn't the trip to Mount Bei your idea?

468
00:22:16,200 --> 00:22:17,790
Now the envoy delegation is missing,

469
00:22:17,790 --> 00:22:19,480
the Empress Dowager
and the Emperor are missing,

470
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:21,610
and even His Highness isn't seeing us.

471
00:22:21,640 --> 00:22:22,700
This isn't normal.

472
00:22:23,310 --> 00:22:24,000
Indeed.

473
00:22:24,190 --> 00:22:24,770
Lord Jia,

474
00:22:25,200 --> 00:22:26,000
wait a moment.

475
00:22:26,350 --> 00:22:27,150
Wait a moment.

476
00:22:27,910 --> 00:22:28,310
You...

477
00:22:29,590 --> 00:22:30,750
Will His Highness see him?

478
00:22:30,750 --> 00:22:31,790
Is he allowed in?

479
00:22:31,830 --> 00:22:32,470
Yes.

480
00:22:37,440 --> 00:22:38,070
Mr. Xu.

481
00:22:39,520 --> 00:22:41,120
Let me ask one more question.

482
00:22:42,110 --> 00:22:43,210
Has Prince Duan

483
00:22:43,880 --> 00:22:45,930
left any private message for me?

484
00:22:46,240 --> 00:22:47,440
If anything happens,

485
00:22:47,720 --> 00:22:49,850
all of you will certainly be notified.

486
00:22:51,310 --> 00:22:52,230
Wait, Mr. Xu.

487
00:22:53,240 --> 00:22:54,550
You may not know me.

488
00:22:55,440 --> 00:22:57,200
You should go back and wait for news,

489
00:22:57,200 --> 00:22:57,930
Lord Murong.

490
00:23:00,110 --> 00:23:01,250
M-Mr. Xu!

491
00:23:17,400 --> 00:23:18,480
In the battle at the posthouse,

492
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:19,550
I witnessed with my own eyes

493
00:23:19,550 --> 00:23:21,280
Tu'er and his men's abilities.

494
00:23:21,310 --> 00:23:24,270
Each of them could really fight 10 men
on their own and were incredibly brave.

495
00:23:24,270 --> 00:23:27,110
Logically,
with the skills of the Emperor's guards,

496
00:23:27,110 --> 00:23:28,770
they wouldn't have survived.

497
00:24:44,880 --> 00:24:46,410
There was a master fighter?

498
00:24:54,160 --> 00:24:56,010
I'm willing to help with all my strength.

499
00:24:56,010 --> 00:24:57,680
[Since that's the case,
I'm willing to help with all my strength]

500
00:24:56,270 --> 00:24:57,700
The experts around the Emperor

501
00:24:57,700 --> 00:24:59,990
[The experts around the Emperor
you mentioned—I've identified them]

502
00:24:57,960 --> 00:24:59,200
you mentioned—

503
00:24:59,830 --> 00:25:01,090
I've identified them.

504
00:25:01,350 --> 00:25:02,960
That little fox Yu Wanyin.

505
00:25:04,750 --> 00:25:06,030
She tricked me again.

506
00:25:07,270 --> 00:25:08,130
Your Highness,

507
00:25:08,160 --> 00:25:10,400
I carefully examined all the traces.

508
00:25:11,750 --> 00:25:13,550
There was indeed a master fighter.

509
00:25:13,550 --> 00:25:14,080
However,

510
00:25:14,510 --> 00:25:16,510
apart from this one person,
the others seem

511
00:25:16,510 --> 00:25:18,550
no match for the envoy delegation.

512
00:25:23,510 --> 00:25:24,910
Could there be something

513
00:25:26,240 --> 00:25:27,570
that we've overlooked?

514
00:25:50,160 --> 00:25:52,090
The smell of saltpeter and sulfur?

515
00:25:58,570 --> 00:26:00,300
It seems this is how the Emperor

516
00:26:01,480 --> 00:26:03,590
managed to escape.

517
00:26:07,640 --> 00:26:09,160
Hurry up!

518
00:26:10,110 --> 00:26:10,920
Don't push me!

519
00:26:13,400 --> 00:26:13,800
Hurry!

520
00:26:20,960 --> 00:26:21,760
I'm not going.

521
00:26:22,440 --> 00:26:24,010
As the Prince of Yan State,

522
00:26:24,590 --> 00:26:26,300
I'm wearing eunuch's clothes,

523
00:26:26,300 --> 00:26:28,490
living in a tunnel like a rat.

524
00:26:28,590 --> 00:26:29,760
What a disgrace!

525
00:26:29,880 --> 00:26:32,680
In this palace,
besides His Majesty, it's all eunuchs.

526
00:26:32,680 --> 00:26:33,400
Should I give you

527
00:26:33,400 --> 00:26:34,160
a dragon robe?

528
00:26:34,160 --> 00:26:34,560
You...

529
00:26:34,960 --> 00:26:35,420
Come on.

530
00:26:35,480 --> 00:26:36,830
You could dress like a woman,

531
00:26:36,830 --> 00:26:37,850
just like me.

532
00:26:37,980 --> 00:26:40,440
You Great Xia people
are just unreasonable.

533
00:26:40,640 --> 00:26:41,270
What now?

534
00:26:41,350 --> 00:26:42,870
Want me to beat you up again?

535
00:26:42,870 --> 00:26:43,630
Pick it up!

536
00:26:44,630 --> 00:26:45,190
Move!

537
00:26:45,550 --> 00:26:47,400
Do you want His majesty to wait for you?

538
00:26:47,400 --> 00:26:47,930
Hurry up!

539
00:26:55,200 --> 00:26:56,340
Search thoroughly!

540
00:26:56,550 --> 00:26:57,410
Your Highness.

541
00:26:57,680 --> 00:27:01,030
That person was one of the Imperial Guards
who rescued the Emperor that day.

542
00:27:01,030 --> 00:27:01,960
He's one of ours.

543
00:27:05,440 --> 00:27:06,550
Greetings, Prince Duan.

544
00:27:06,550 --> 00:27:08,010
When you arrived that day,

545
00:27:08,880 --> 00:27:11,540
how many people
were in the underground palace?

546
00:27:11,830 --> 00:27:12,550
My rank...

547
00:27:13,480 --> 00:27:14,540
wasn't high enough

548
00:27:14,590 --> 00:27:15,320
to get close.

549
00:27:15,880 --> 00:27:17,240
But according to those who saw,

550
00:27:17,240 --> 00:27:18,920
there were only the Emperor,
the Empress Dowager,

551
00:27:18,920 --> 00:27:20,640
two severely wounded guards,

552
00:27:21,830 --> 00:27:23,210
and a maid.

553
00:27:24,680 --> 00:27:25,510
No one else?

554
00:27:26,110 --> 00:27:27,710
There was indeed no one else.

555
00:27:29,510 --> 00:27:30,110
You may go.

556
00:27:30,550 --> 00:27:30,920
Yes.

557
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:36,940
It seems that although

558
00:27:37,720 --> 00:27:40,180
the Emperor
had a master fighter and weapons

559
00:27:40,350 --> 00:27:41,090
around him,

560
00:27:42,640 --> 00:27:44,440
they didn't gain any advantage.

561
00:27:45,830 --> 00:27:48,350
Otherwise, he wouldn't have escaped
to this underground palace.

562
00:27:48,350 --> 00:27:48,750
So...

563
00:27:49,350 --> 00:27:51,480
shall I proceed according to the plan?

564
00:27:51,720 --> 00:27:52,480
Plans

565
00:27:53,510 --> 00:27:55,040
can't keep up with changes.

566
00:27:56,030 --> 00:27:58,030
Right now, the most important thing

567
00:27:58,550 --> 00:28:00,180
is to find Tu'er first.

568
00:28:05,480 --> 00:28:07,110
But where has he gone?

569
00:28:27,030 --> 00:28:28,030
I'm worried about

570
00:28:30,000 --> 00:28:31,460
what identity I should use

571
00:28:31,510 --> 00:28:32,770
to ally with Great Xia.

572
00:28:33,240 --> 00:28:35,040
If I declare myself the new king,

573
00:28:35,440 --> 00:28:37,240
wouldn't the people of Yan State

574
00:28:37,640 --> 00:28:38,510
see me as a traitor?

575
00:28:38,510 --> 00:28:39,310
Of course not.

576
00:28:42,550 --> 00:28:45,920
You're the envoy sent specifically
by the Emperor of Yan for the peace talks.

577
00:28:45,920 --> 00:28:46,700
Doesn't that

578
00:28:47,110 --> 00:28:49,570
make your signing official and legitimate?

579
00:28:50,240 --> 00:28:51,530
I'm an impostor.

580
00:28:51,750 --> 00:28:53,210
But the people don't know.

581
00:28:54,030 --> 00:28:54,630
Tomorrow,

582
00:28:55,120 --> 00:28:56,580
once the treaty is signed,

583
00:28:57,310 --> 00:28:59,170
I'll immediately spread the news

584
00:28:59,590 --> 00:29:00,980
across the country,

585
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:03,010
all the way to Yan State.

586
00:29:03,960 --> 00:29:04,480
I'll say

587
00:29:05,110 --> 00:29:07,440
that Zhaluowahan showed great sincerity

588
00:29:07,510 --> 00:29:08,570
by sending a prince

589
00:29:09,310 --> 00:29:10,550
for the peace talks,

590
00:29:11,510 --> 00:29:13,680
and Great Xia,
appreciating that sincerity,

591
00:29:13,680 --> 00:29:15,810
honored you as a distinguished guest.

592
00:29:16,110 --> 00:29:17,240
Then the two nations

593
00:29:17,350 --> 00:29:19,280
have finally ceased hostilities.

594
00:29:19,310 --> 00:29:21,510
The people of Yan State, weary from war,

595
00:29:22,000 --> 00:29:23,060
will also rejoice.

596
00:29:24,590 --> 00:29:25,350
By then...

597
00:29:25,750 --> 00:29:27,080
By then, if Zhaluowahan

598
00:29:29,270 --> 00:29:30,960
refuses to acknowledge the treaty

599
00:29:30,960 --> 00:29:32,310
just to start the war,

600
00:29:33,070 --> 00:29:34,740
he'll be breaking his word

601
00:29:36,200 --> 00:29:38,000
and proving himself an unjust ruler.

602
00:29:38,000 --> 00:29:38,860
I didn't expect

603
00:29:39,240 --> 00:29:40,700
you'd catch on so quickly.

604
00:29:48,360 --> 00:29:50,090
I'll take that as a compliment.

605
00:29:51,200 --> 00:29:52,830
Based on what I know about him,

606
00:29:52,830 --> 00:29:54,630
he won't sit back and do nothing.

607
00:29:54,640 --> 00:29:54,920
I...

608
00:29:58,880 --> 00:30:01,140
I don't want to see civil war
in Yan State.

609
00:30:01,430 --> 00:30:02,960
If we are to kill Zhaluowahan,

610
00:30:02,960 --> 00:30:04,290
it must be done quickly.

611
00:30:05,320 --> 00:30:06,580
I can lend you some men.

612
00:30:09,160 --> 00:30:09,960
It's settled.

613
00:30:10,160 --> 00:30:10,890
I'm leaving.

614
00:30:26,110 --> 00:30:28,010
Can I not stay down here?

615
00:30:28,310 --> 00:30:28,880
No.

616
00:30:29,590 --> 00:30:31,370
Can he at least not stay with me?

617
00:30:31,750 --> 00:30:32,500
No.

618
00:30:36,640 --> 00:30:37,110
Can I...

619
00:30:37,110 --> 00:30:38,170
Just go down there!

620
00:30:39,760 --> 00:30:40,670
We're both men.

621
00:30:40,720 --> 00:30:41,790
What's there to be awkward about?

622
00:30:41,790 --> 00:30:42,990
Stop talking so much.

623
00:30:59,200 --> 00:31:00,830
Stop pretending to be asleep.

624
00:31:00,830 --> 00:31:02,960
The bed is shaking from your laughter.

625
00:31:03,880 --> 00:31:05,880
Making Tu'er pretend to be a eunuch?

626
00:31:05,920 --> 00:31:07,920
I can't believe you came up with that.

627
00:31:07,920 --> 00:31:09,120
I learned it from you.

628
00:31:10,430 --> 00:31:12,290
Having Eunuch An impersonate me?

629
00:31:13,550 --> 00:31:17,080
Eunuch An is still hanging around
the Empress Dowager's place.

630
00:31:17,440 --> 00:31:18,350
The men you said

631
00:31:18,510 --> 00:31:19,830
you'd lend him just now—

632
00:31:19,830 --> 00:31:20,560
was that Bai?

633
00:31:26,030 --> 00:31:26,560
Correct.

634
00:31:27,070 --> 00:31:28,130
Ten points for you.

635
00:31:29,750 --> 00:31:31,440
But as just a martial artist,

636
00:31:31,830 --> 00:31:33,830
can he summon so many people at once?

637
00:31:38,240 --> 00:31:38,720
Wrong.

638
00:31:39,350 --> 00:31:39,880
Minus 10.

639
00:31:40,890 --> 00:31:41,830
What's wrong?

640
00:31:41,920 --> 00:31:44,120
Why do you always bring up other people?

641
00:31:46,160 --> 00:31:47,350
Stop flirting with me.

642
00:31:47,350 --> 00:31:49,550
Keep that up, and your wound will split.

643
00:31:53,200 --> 00:31:53,930
I don't care.

644
00:31:55,750 --> 00:31:57,880
I have something important to ask you.

645
00:31:59,160 --> 00:32:01,460
How do you know so much about Shanyi?

646
00:32:02,440 --> 00:32:03,400
Weren't you

647
00:32:03,590 --> 00:32:05,050
not even here at that time?

648
00:32:09,000 --> 00:32:09,930
I investigated.

649
00:32:10,520 --> 00:32:13,380
The palace servants who recovered
her body told me.

650
00:32:14,070 --> 00:32:16,070
Then, after you recognized
Tu'er in the main hall,

651
00:32:16,070 --> 00:32:18,270
why didn't you confront him immediately?

652
00:32:18,270 --> 00:32:19,480
That might have prevented

653
00:32:19,480 --> 00:32:21,480
that fierce battle on the mountain.

654
00:32:24,400 --> 00:32:26,460
He wouldn't accept a one-sided story

655
00:32:26,680 --> 00:32:27,810
without witnesses.

656
00:32:28,720 --> 00:32:30,780
I had to wait until his efforts failed

657
00:32:30,830 --> 00:32:32,630
and he refused to accept defeat,

658
00:32:33,920 --> 00:32:35,910
so I could give him a new purpose

659
00:32:36,160 --> 00:32:37,890
and someone to take revenge on.

660
00:32:45,920 --> 00:32:47,580
Tu'er's men killed Wang Zhao.

661
00:32:48,270 --> 00:32:49,930
I don't feel sympathy for him.

662
00:32:50,830 --> 00:32:52,290
But his story with Shanyi

663
00:32:52,350 --> 00:32:53,750
is quite heartbreaking.

664
00:32:55,200 --> 00:32:56,000
In this world,

665
00:32:57,270 --> 00:32:58,670
surviving is sheer luck,

666
00:32:59,400 --> 00:33:00,600
and staying together

667
00:33:01,440 --> 00:33:02,900
is an even greater luxury.

668
00:33:12,960 --> 00:33:13,400
Yes.

669
00:33:16,030 --> 00:33:17,560
Being able to stay together

670
00:33:18,350 --> 00:33:19,480
is already a luxury.

671
00:33:20,920 --> 00:33:22,200
So, in a way,

672
00:33:23,270 --> 00:33:24,930
I should be grateful for this.

673
00:33:25,960 --> 00:33:28,590
Otherwise, if we kept
circling around like this,

674
00:33:28,590 --> 00:33:30,190
one day we might suddenly die

675
00:33:30,750 --> 00:33:32,810
without ever really being together.

676
00:33:38,830 --> 00:33:40,310
So...

677
00:33:42,790 --> 00:33:44,510
we are together now?

678
00:33:47,680 --> 00:33:48,550
Oh my.

679
00:33:50,030 --> 00:33:52,160
I've become love-obsessed after all.

680
00:33:56,000 --> 00:33:56,560
But

681
00:33:57,200 --> 00:33:59,330
having witnessed how fragile life is,

682
00:33:59,880 --> 00:34:00,960
I had

683
00:34:01,350 --> 00:34:03,070
the impulse to seize the day.

684
00:34:08,480 --> 00:34:09,540
I feel the same way.

685
00:34:17,480 --> 00:34:18,770
Before you went up the mountain,

686
00:34:18,770 --> 00:34:20,090
didn't you set a flag?

687
00:34:20,400 --> 00:34:22,060
What were you going to tell me?

688
00:34:27,030 --> 00:34:27,830
What's wrong?

689
00:34:30,030 --> 00:34:32,090
I think my wound is really splitting.

690
00:34:32,190 --> 00:34:34,440
I told you not to flirt with me.
You didn't listen.

691
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:35,199
Wait here.

692
00:34:35,280 --> 00:34:36,540
I'll get the medicine.

693
00:34:38,550 --> 00:34:39,210
Don't move.

694
00:34:43,480 --> 00:34:43,960
Wanyin,

695
00:34:45,150 --> 00:34:47,280
I've lost the courage to tell you again.

696
00:34:47,280 --> 00:34:47,880
I'm sorry.
